flowchart LR
    REQ[New user message] --> WHICH{v1 or v2?}
    WHICH -->|v1| H1[ChatHistory.aget_messages]
    WHICH -->|v1| C1[checkpointer.aget v1]
    WHICH -->|v2| CP[checkpointer.aget v2]
    H1 & C1 --> MERGE1[Reduction history of chat]
    CP --> MERGE2[Full prior messages]
    MERGE1 --> RETR[search_agents]
    MERGE2 --> RETR
    MERGE1 --> SUP[Supervisor / DeepAgent]
    MERGE2 --> SUP
    SUP --> SUM[SummarizationMiddleware]
    SUM --> LLM[Bedrock]
